| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2422 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1e4cf86a-38d7-5adb-9cf4-f674cc40130f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
